Error: Error: "Server Creation Has Failed. You Have Reached The Maximum Number Of Servers That You Can Create."

Solution: 1. First, confirm that you have indeed reached the maximum number of servers allowed on your plan. Check your plan details to see how many servers you are allowed to create.
2. If you have reached the maximum, consider upgrading your plan to allow for more server creation.
3. If you are not able to upgrade, consider deleting some of your old servers to make space for new
